entry.title: Cedar Rapids Wants to Take These Homes---Before the Floods Do
entry.content: In Cedar Rapids’ Time Check neighborhood, some homeowners are “paying the price for the safety of the entire city,” mayor says.

entry.title: Blasts Hit Russia-Controlled City in Ukraine on Supply Route to Crimea
entry.content: The strikes on Melitopol make strategic sense, analysts say, because they could help to break through Russia’s land bridge and restore Ukraine’s access to the Azov Sea.
